#: ../../whitepaper/summary.rst:2
msgid "Summary"
msgstr "摘要"

#: ../../whitepaper/summary.rst:4
msgid ""
"We are reconstructing the transport layer of the Internet, we are re-"
"defining the Internet. Each user and each terminal is no longer just the "
"bottom layer of the food chain, but should be the provider and co-builder of"
" the Internet and services."
msgstr "我们正在重构互联网传输层协议，我们正在重新定义互联网。每个用户和每个终端不再仅仅是食物链的底层，而应该是互联网和服务的提供者和共同建设者。"

#: ../../whitepaper/summary.rst:9
msgid ""
"The Vision Network is a set of infrastructure for building a decentralized "
"Internet. It is a distributed extensible virtual network, based on the "
"physical network layer and the ISP network layer."
msgstr "Vision Network 远景网络是构建去中心化互联网的一系列基础设施。是在物理网络层、ISP 网络层之上构建的分布式智能虚拟网络。"

#: ../../whitepaper/summary.rst:13
msgid ""
"Vision Network uses blockchain technology, distributed networks and "
"asymmetric encryption, provides distributed services such as Auto-Proxy, "
"multi-layer anonymous network, IM, non-polluted DNS, even CDN and DDoS "
"defense, etc."
msgstr ""
"Vision Network 远景网络使用区块链、分布式网络和非对称加密等技术，提供一系列分布式服务，如自动代理服务、多层匿名网络、 IM "
"即时通信、无污染的 DNS 解析，甚至是 CDN 内容加速分发和 DDoS 防御等。"

#: ../../whitepaper/summary.rst:17
msgid ""
"The :ref:`voken` with stable value scale will be used in the entire ecology "
"and produce an incentive effect. Everyone can participate in distributed "
"network construction. We believe the Vision Network will make the future "
"Internet more open, more equal, more stable, more efficient, safer and "
"freer."
msgstr ""
"使用价值尺度稳定的 :ref:`voken` "
"作为生态“货币”激励，是由全球无限节点参与构建的、具有成长性的分布式互联网基础设施，使互联网更开放、更平等、更稳定、更高效、更安全、更自由。"
